      "id": "PopularPost90292",
      "post_content": "A friend of mine held off a [Grave Titan](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Grave Titan) with one of these at the Prerelease. Killing the titan + wipe out the zombies + comes back next turn all made it quite unfavorable for his opponent to attack. Shame about the high cost to return, though.",
