      "id": "PopularPost89810",
      "post_content": "This is essentially a tweak of [Shard Phoenix](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Shard Phoenix) for the same CC. The extra power and toughness and additional point of damage are nice, but the much greater cost to return it as well as the fact that you can't sacrifice it whenever you want probably make it somewhat worse.",
